    <h7> The species of bears </h7>
<p>There are only eight species of bears in the world which are:</p>
<ul>  
    <li>Asiatic black bears (also called moon bears)</li>
    <li>brown bears (which include grizzly bears)</li>
    <li>giant pandas</li>
    <li>North American black bears</li>
    <li> polar bears</li>
    <li>sloth bears</li>
    <li>spectacled bears (also called Andean bears)</li>
    <li>sun bears.</li>
</ul>

